title: Warped - Gay Normality and Queer Anti-Capitalism (2015) Gooner
description:
Warped - Gay Normality and Queer Anti-Capitalism (2015).pdf Gooner

Publisher: Brill Academic Publishers; Lam edition (February 17, 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 9004223916
ISBN-13: 978-9004223912

"Warped" shows how the successive 'same-sex economies' of the past century and a half have led to both gay 'normality' and queer resistance. It sees sexual rebellions and queer social justice struggles as harbingers of a queer anti-capitalism
